                <h1>MLA Citation for "The Yellow Wallpaper" - Guide</h1>
                <p>To cite "The Yellow Wallpaper" by Charlotte Perkins Gilman in MLA format, use the following format: Gilman, Charlotte Perkins. "The Yellow Wallpaper." *The Complete Works of Charlotte Perkins Gilman*, edited by Dale M. Bauer, University of Alabama Press, 2009, pp. 227-248. Remember to italicize the book title and include page numbers as necessary.</p>
